item.title: Bragar Eagel & Squire, P.C. Is Investigating Thoughtworks, Chemours, Methanex, and Inari Medical and Encourages Investors to Contact the Firm
item.description: NEW YORK, March 08, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Bragar Eagel & Squire, P.C., a nationally recognized shareholder rights law firm, is investigating potential claims against Thoughtworks Holding, Inc. (NASDAQ: TWKS), The Chemours Company (NYSE: CC), Methanex Corporation (NASDAQ: MEOH), and Inari Medical, Inc. (NASDAQ: NARI). Our investigations concern whether these companies have violated the federal securities laws and/or engaged in other unlawful business practices. Additional information about each case can be found at the link provided.
